title: Flux Family Secrets v1.0.0 Android
description:
Fix the errors in time in this exciting Hidden Object game and take your rightful place in the Flux family! Explore famous historical sites like Hatshepsut's tomb, the Wright Brothers' workshop, Benjamin Franklin's study and many more. Flux Family Secrets: The Ripple Effect has you realign the timeline by finding misplaced objects scattered through time and solving clever puzzles.

Features:
Relaxed mode.
Get help! Optional tutorial and hints with auto recharge.
Visual object list.
Collectible inventory and toolkit objects.
Beautiful High-resolution graphics.
Explore scenes in close up with integrated pinch zoom magnification
Required Android O/S : 2.3+
